TEXT 128 264 Left 2 ;This file is an example simulation of one side of the H bridge. A 9.6V battery is used\nwhile one signal pin is PWM'd at 90% 1khz and the other signal pin is left open. \nLibraries for the LM324, IRF4905, and IRLZ44N are needed.
